    "Ye et al. [261] investigated the joint active and passive beamforming design for IRS-aided ISAC systems, and trained a CNN in a USL manner to learn the mappings from the channel samples to the corresponding beamforming vectors.",
    "Compared with iterative algorithms, their DL-based scheme enjoyed competitive performance with lower computational complexity.",
    "Eghbali et al. [262] investigated the joint beamforming and phase-shift design for simultaneously transmitting and reflecting IRS-aided ISAC networks with moving targets and users, where the sum of achievable rate and sensing power was maximized.",
